data.description: METICULOUSLY MAINTAINED TOWNHOME IN 34110! ZONED SINGLE FAMILY CAN GO FHA/VA. Located in the coveted Milano community in North Naples. Just a few minutes from the beautiful beaches, dining options, shopping, and entertainment. Enjoy a prime location in the heart of Naples, while taking in the beautiful sunsets from the private lanai. Recent upgrades include new lanai screens and a newer roof, ensuring your comfort and peace of mind. The exterior has been refreshed with a fresh coat of paint. Your convenience is assured with a 1-car garage for everyday ease. What sets this community apart are the low HOA fees, providing access to amenities like a community pool/spa, dog park, tennis, and pickleball courts. This townhouse is also conveniently located just minutes away from highly-rated educational institutions such as Veterans Memorial Elementary, North Naples Middle, and the recently established Aubrey Rogers High School. The best part about this property is the quick and easy access to I-75, making commuting a breeze. Just 6 miles away from the Wiggins State Park Beach and only 1 mile to Seed To Table shopping and dining options. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your own!
